# Ownership

- `web` owns `apps/web/**`
- `api` owns `apps/api/**`
- `packages/shared/**` is FROZEN — Project-Lead-gated, change via proposal only
- No agent commits outside its owned paths.
- Cross-boundary or contract change → proposal → Project Lead decision.
